  "description": {
    "zh": "我又有任务给你，那位买了一堆注射器的客户对这些产品非常满意，现在又下了一单。\n\n你愿意继续吗？他这次胃口更大了，而且他还要求更昂贵更稀有的注射器，不过别担心时间，士兵，他说他可以等。\n\n寻找这些注射器可以去TerraGroupTerraGroup集团实验室看看，那可能是个好地方。我能想象你在那里能找到多少稀有的注射器……\n\n祝你好运，士兵！",
    "en": "I got something for you again, the guy who bought a ordered a bunch of injectors from us was so satisfied with them that he is asking for another batch.\n\nCan I count on you again? This time even more expensive and rare ones, don't worry about time however soldier, we were told that he can wait for them.\n\nSearching for these injectors inside the Terragroup laboratory might be the way to go here, at least that would have been my plan. I can only assume the amount of rare injectors that you could find in that place...\nAnyway good luck soldier!"
  },
